HOME_DELIVERY.pricing: Cijena usluge dostave nije uračunata u cijenu proizvoda.

weekend_delivery.days: Dostava proizvoda Kupcu obavlja se isključivo radnim danom. Subote, nedjelje, blagdani i neradni dani ne računaju se u rok dostave.

SUMMARY:
DELIVERY OPTIONS: The store offers home delivery via unnamed courier services and personal in-store pickup. Parcel shop and locker delivery are not available.
PRICING: Delivery costs are not included in the product price and are not specified. No free shipping threshold is mentioned. In-store pickup is available as an alternative.
DELIVERY TIME & RESTRICTIONS: Standard delivery takes 3-5 working days. Deliveries are made only on weekdays to the entrance of the building. There is no information on island surcharges or express delivery.
NOTABLE FEATURES: In-store pickup is available at their showroom in Zagreb (Ilica 11), including on Saturdays.
WEBSITE ASSESSMENT: The shipping information is very basic. It confirms the availability of home delivery and in-store pickup but lacks essential details such as shipping costs, specific courier partners, and policies for island delivery or COD surcharges. All information is located on a single 'Dostava i povrat proizvoda' page.
